version_description: I believe this is the simplest way to achieve the correct chord and bass note progressions on guitar.

Very detailed version taken from original way Gerry Leonard used to play live with David Bowie. Version taken from video which guitarrist Gerry Leonard shows how he adapted the studio version (when David Bowie asked him to play it live) with a guitar. Video of Gerry Leonard explaining: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JVN-CuCfrM (He starts talking at 10:25) Live performance for reference: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DBwN2Ve9Mc.
The "B C D" is a walk up.
It's a different version of the song from the game 'Omikron: The Nomad Soul'.
